title: Maddox - The Alphabet of Manliness
description:
This is a must read, laugh your ass off!

In June 2006, Maddox&#039;s first book, The Alphabet of Manliness, was published. It reached the number one spot on the Amazon.com sales chart. The book is illustrated and its format is a chapter-length entry for each letter in the English alphabet regarding a "manly" topic (for example, N is for Chuck Norris).

If you want to know more about maddox check out http://maddox.xmission.com, the best page in the universe, or http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maddox_(writer) to read his bio on wikipedia.

Dont forget that: When you don&#039;t seed, a little kitten dies.

Enjoy!
